<section id="faq" class="section s-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="slabel">Questions</div>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq">
      <details><summary>What's the dress code?</summary><div>Dress to impress for the nightclub. No flip-flops, sports jerseys, workout clothes, baseball caps, or offensive imagery. Smart casual or club attire works. No dress code to board the bus.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Is our group kept completely private?</summary><div>100%. Your group is never paired with strangers. Private bus, private lounge, private nightclub entry — the entire night is exclusively yours.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can we bring our own drinks (BYOB)?</summary><div>Yes — BYOB friendly on the bus. We also provide complimentary champagne, mixers, cups, straws, napkins, and fresh ice. Drink responsibly.</div></details>
      <details><summary>What if someone is under 21?</summary><div>All participants must be 21+ with valid ID, checked at three points. Exception: 21st birthday guests welcome if the reservation starts at midnight or later.</div></details>
      <details><summary>How far in advance should we book?</summary><div>1–2 weeks for regular weekends. For major events (EDC, Memorial Day, 4th of July, NYE) book 4–6 weeks ahead — those dates sell out fast.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can we choose which nightclub?</summary><div>You can express a preference and we'll do our best. Clubs rotate by day. Use the Club Finder above to see what's typically open on your date.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Where do you pick us up?</summary><div>Hotels, lounges, and event locations across Las Vegas, Henderson, Summerlin, and North Las Vegas. Off-Strip and Airbnb pickups accommodated.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can we split the payment?</summary><div>Yes — payment splits up to 3 ways. Contact us for custom arrangements for larger groups.</div></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

